(xi)          Seller is duly organized, validly existing and in good standing under the laws of the jurisdiction of its organization.  Seller has all necessary power and authority to enter into this Agreement and to consummate all of the transactions contemplated herein, the individuals executing this Agreement on behalf of Seller are duly authorized to execute, deliver and perform this Agreement on behalf of Seller and to bind Seller, and this Agreement and all documents to be executed by Seller and delivered to Purchaser hereunder (A) are and will be the legal, valid and binding obligations of Seller, enforceable in accordance with their terms, and (B) do not or will not contravene any provision of Seller’s organizational documents or any existing laws and regulations
 applicable to Seller or the Property;
 
